                     <interp inst="t18290219-35-person395" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopaman to a pawnbroker. A suit of mourning was pawned with me on the 15th of January, by the prisoner, in the name of 
               <persName id="t18290219-35-person396">
                  Ann 
                  Weston
               <interp inst="t18290219-35-person396" type="surname" value="Weston"></interp>
